 bout against Janjaem Suwannapheng from Thailand to reach the Olympics final.Her reaction is priceless.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.69314345281196, \"rank\": 0.4167878525628076, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"66kg bout\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"Janjaem Suwannapheng\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"Her reaction\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"May your glory be eternal sister!!\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your glory\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"eternal sister\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"!pic.twitter.com/5iyiS85mtO 'I do not care what anyone is saying about me with the controversy,' Khelif said.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'All that is important to me is that I stay on the level and give my people the performance they deserve.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the level\", \